<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover" />
  <title>About Us | ElectroScan AI — Intelligence That Powers Electrical Safety</title>
  <!-- Google Fonts + premium typography -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:opsz,wght@14..32,300;14..32,400;14..32,500;14..32,600;14..32,700;14..32,800&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <!-- Font Awesome 6 (pro style) -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" />
    
</head>
<body>

<main>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="reveal">Intelligence That Powers<br>Electrical Safety</h1>
      <p class="reveal">We're transforming electrical inspections with precision AI — making every building safer through intelligent automation, predictive analytics, and unmatched accuracy.</p>
      <div class="reveal">
         <a asp-action="mission" asp-controller="Home" class="btn-premium"><i class="fas fa-play-circle"></i> See Our Mission</a>
         <a asp-action="Team" asp-controller="Home" class="btn-premium btn-outline-premium" style="margin-top: 16px;">Meet the Team →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Mission / Vision / Values cards -->
  <div class="container reveal">
    <div class="mission-grid">
      <div class="mission-card">
        <div class="mission-icon"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div>
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>Make every electrical system safer through intelligence — eliminating preventable failures before they cause harm.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mission-card">
        <div class="mission-icon"><i class="fas fa-globe-americas"></i></div>
        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
        <p>A world where no building fire, outage, or electrical hazard is caused by an issue that could have been detected in advance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mission-card">
        <div class="mission-icon"><i class="fas fa-hand-sparkles"></i></div>
        <h3>Our Values</h3>
        <p>Precision over speed. Transparency over shortcuts. Safety above all — for the professionals who depend on us and the people they protect.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Story + stats (matching index premium) -->
  <div class="container story-section reveal">
    <div class="split-layout">
      <div class="split-text">
        <span style="color:#1F8A6B; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:1px;">OUR STORY</span>
        <h2>Built to close a <span style="color:#1F8A6B;">critical gap</span></h2>
        <p style="color:#334155; line-height:1.7;">ElectroScan AI was founded by a team of electrical engineers and AI specialists who saw what traditional inspection methods were missing. Inspections were slow, prone to human error, and blind to failures before they happened.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:16px; color:#4A6B5E;">We built an intelligent platform combining computer vision, machine learning, and deep electrical expertise — trained on millions of real-world scenarios to deliver inspection accuracy the industry had never seen.</p>
        <div class="stats-row">
          <div class="stat-block"><h4>2024</h4><span style="color:#5A7568;">Founded</span></div>
          <div class="stat-block"><h4>50K+</h4><span style="color:#5A7568;">Scans completed</span></div>
          <div class="stat-block"><h4>99.9%</h4><span style="color:#5A7568;">Detection accuracy</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="split-media">
        <img src="~/Image/about.jpg" alt="About ElectroScan AI" style="width:100%; border-radius: 32px; box-shadow: 0 12px 24px -8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);" />
        <p style="margin-top: 24px; font-weight:500;">AI-driven electrical diagnostics</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Why choose us (values grid) -->
  <div class="container values-section reveal">
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <span style="color:#1F8A6B; font-weight:600;">WHY ELECTROSCAN AI</span>
      <h2 style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-top: 12px;">Industry-leading technology <br>meets <span style="color:#1F8A6B;">electrical expertise</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i></div>
        <h4>AI-Powered Analysis</h4>
        <p>Advanced neural networks trained on millions of electrical scenarios — detecting issues humans routinely miss.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-calculator"></i></div>
        <h4>Smart Calculations</h4>
        <p>Automated load calculations and wire sizing based on real-world NEC standards. Zero manual math required.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i></div>
        <h4>Compliance Reports</h4>
        <p>Comprehensive, compliance-ready reports generated instantly — shareable with clients and authorities.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Leadership team -->
  <div class="container reveal">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">
      <span style="color:#1F8A6B; font-weight:600;">THE EXPERTS BEHIND THE AI</span>
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem;">Leadership & innovation</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="team-grid">
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="team-avatar"><i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i></div>
        <h4>Dr. Sarah Chen</h4>
        <span style="color:#1F8A6B; font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:600;">CTO, AI Research Lead</span>
        <p style="margin-top: 16px; color:#5A7568;">15+ years in machine learning and computer vision applied to industrial systems.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="team-avatar"><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i></div>
        <h4>Michael Rodriguez</h4>
        <span style="color:#1F8A6B; font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:600;">Head of Engineering</span>
        <p style="margin-top: 16px; color:#5A7568;">Licensed Master Electrician with 20+ years designing large-scale electrical systems.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="team-avatar"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></div>
        <h4>Emily Watson</h4>
        <span style="color:#1F8A6B; font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:600;">Safety Director</span>
        <p style="margin-top: 16px; color:#5A7568;">Certified Safety Professional, NEC compliance expert and risk auditing specialist.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA section (connect) -->
  <div class="container cta-about reveal">
    <h2 style="font-size: 2rem;">Ready to transform your inspections?</h2>
    <p style="margin: 20px auto; max-width: 550px; opacity:0.9;">Join thousands of electrical professionals using AI to work smarter, safer, and faster — starting today.</p>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a asp-action="services" asp-controller="Home" asp-fragment="ai-scan" class="btn-premium" style="background: white; color: #0B2B26;"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Start AI Scan</a>
      <a asp-action="contact" asp-controller="Home" class="btn-premium btn-outline-premium" style="border-color:white; color:white; background:transparent;">Contact Sales →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
    <script src="~/js/site.js" defer></script>

</body>
</html>